Title: Plan a new trip

Primary Actors: User
Secondary Actors: -

Preconditions: -
Postconditions: A mobilephone.

Flow:
1. The user enters the information about a city he/she wants to enter
2. the system responds with the specific date
3. the user enters the time he/she wants to stay at the destination
4. the user enters with which different mobility things he/she wants to travel
5. the system responds with a planned trip


Alternative flows:
-

Information Requirements: User-ID, Destination, length, allowed mobility